### P5 ‚Äî VCF/BCF Reader (Planned)

| Plan | Title | Depends On | Status |
|------|-------|-----------|--------|
| P5-001 | read_vcf via plink-ng per-line parsers | P2 (shared infra) | Planned |

Issue: #11. Uses plink-ng's battle-tested per-line VCF parsing functions
(script-extracted from `plink2_import.cc`) combined with plink2_text streaming
I/O (already compiled in pgenlib lib) for fast libdeflate BGZF decompression.
See `P5-001-read-vcf` for full design.

Key decisions:
- **Parser**: Script-based extraction of ~1,420 lines of per-line parsers
  from plink-ng submodule (reproducible sync on pin updates)
- **I/O**: plink2_text + plink2_bgzf (already compiled, libdeflate > zlib)
- **Scope**: Phase 1 = text VCF (.vcf/.vcf.gz), Phase 2 = BCF binary

